reviews.text: Great Beijing style food in a cèntric location. Reasonable price. I would recommend the beef rib in garlic sauce (Pic).

This restaurant  is not recommend to everyone who desire tasty food and good service.

The price is expensive but the food is not match with this high price. 

A special discount is offered for my credit card but the cashier try to skip that.

Very nice deco of the store. I love Beijing food, they are not very spicy, peking duck is the MUST you have to order! Also the set dinner is very flexible that you can swap food with the same price, I do recommend you to order the set if you have 4 people or more. Proportion is just right.

Great variety of traditional Beijing foods, Roasted Beijing Duck, Crispy Lamb, Minced pork served with crispy pancakes ……
All tasteful with an old-Beijing feel.
Traditional beijing cuisine.  Nice restaurant

result.name: Beijing Home

reviews.text: Great Beijing style food in a cèntric location. Reasonable price. I would recommend the beef rib in garlic sauce (Pic).

服務差食物一般價錢又唔平。
小籠包唔好味，同鼎泰豐冇得比。
侍應一直吹你嗌餸，態度很差，不會再幫襯。
裝修有特色,食物質素可以。上次去一家人吃晚飯。經歷愉快的一餐。 介紹你試拔絲草莓。
裝修很漂亮,用了北京常見泥磚刻做裝飾,有四張桌子下放了金魚,有趣。

價格與味道都相付，8個人11、12 道菜連小食，每人都係$240，ok 啵.

喜歡那個煎豆腐、地瓜苗、東坡肉也不錯，反填鴨就好似北京樓好食d ，高力豆沙，豆沙就少左一豆沙，水煮魚可以少辣，都唔錯.

還有枱與枱之空間都夠，這方面絕對完勝北京樓👍🏻
